He's very weak.

824
00:57:38,136 --> 00:57:39,364
这边
Here.

825
00:57:41,906 --> 00:57:45,332
去准备热水澡和些干净衣服
I want you to prepare a hot bath and some clean clothes.

826
00:57:46,076 --> 00:57:47,274
再弄点吃的
And something to eat.

827
00:57:47,345 --> 00:57:49,870
这就去  太太
Right away, ma'am.

828
00:58:08,632 --> 00:58:10,523
我的小宝贝都好吗?
How are my little ones?

829
