Daddy!

830
00:58:16,941 --> 00:58:19,142
你怎么去了那么久?
Why did you take so long?

831
00:58:26,150 --> 00:58:27,617
你好  尼古拉斯
Hello, Nicholas.

832
00:58:27,652 --> 00:58:28,880
我说了  是不是
I told you, you see.

833
00:58:28,920 --> 00:58:30,683
我说了他会回来的
I told you he'd come back.

834
00:58:37,762 --> 00:58:39,696
