873
01:00:56,167 --> 01:01:00,160
进房间  今天你没甜点吃
Go to your room. No dessert for you today.

874
01:01:04,008 --> 01:01:08,206
不要哭  不要哭
Ohh, no crying now, no crying.

875
01:01:08,279 --> 01:01:10,247
别哭了
Oh, stop that here.

876
01:01:10,314 --> 01:01:13,750
