All right. I'll be back shortly.

914
01:03:35,560 --> 01:03:37,960
别坐在地上或蹭到墙上
No sitting on the floor or leaning against the walls.

915
01:03:37,995 --> 01:03:39,292
不会的
No.

916
01:03:55,379 --> 01:03:58,348
